Class AppointmentView

java.lang.Object
clinic.cs213project3.view.AppointmentView
public class AppointmentView extends Object
The template class used to display appointment data onto the table view in the UI. The table view under the "Appointments" tab contains six columns, corresponding to each data field. Date fields include date, timeslot, patient, location, room, and cost.
Author:
Aarush Desai
